    "summary": "The user explores the evolving meaning of \"fake news,\" questioning whether the term refers to actual misinformation or is used as a political weapon to discredit unfavorable reporting. The assistant responds by analyzing the rhetorical weaponization of the term and attempts to distinguish between factual inaccuracies and partisan labeling.",
